headline: Stay Ahead of the Game With Lululemon (LULU) Q1 Earnings: Wall Street's Insights on Key Metrics
summary: Looking beyond Wall Street's top -and-bottom-line estimate forecasts for Lululemon (LULU), delve into some of its key metrics to gain a deeper insight into the company's potential performance for the quarter ended April 2025.

headline: 2 Cash-Heavy Stocks for Long-Term Investors and 1 to Be Wary Of
summary: Companies with more cash than debt can be financially resilient, but that doesn’t mean they’re all strong investments. Some lack leverage because they struggle to grow or generate consistent profits, making them unattractive borrowers.
